element_text:
Indtægter af kapitalandele i tilknyttede virksomheder
omfatter den forholdsmæssige andel af de tilknyttede
virksomheders driftsresultat reguleret for interne avancer
og tab.
Income from investments in group enterprises
Income from investments in group enterprises comprises
the pro rata share of the group enterprises' operating
profit/loss adjusted for internal profits and losses.
